Requirement Analysis

Functional Requirements

Features/Components/Modules
Edge Cases

Example
1) Authentication of user whenever he/she logs into the system.
2) System shutdown in case of a cyber attack.
3) A Verification email is sent to user whenever he/she registers for the first time on some software system.


Non Functional Requirements

Scalability
Performance
Redundancy
Consistency - Every request should have same output upon multiple times querying. Internal systems are synchronized
Pluggable

Example
1) Emails should be sent with a latency of no greater than 12 hours from such an activity.
2) The processing of each request should be done within 10 seconds
3) The site should load in 3 seconds when the number of simultaneous users are > 10000
